# Inbox Folder

This folder contains incoming items that need to be processed by AI agents.

## Example Structure

```markdown
---
type: email
from: client@example.com
subject: Project Inquiry
received: 2026-03-09T10:00:00Z
priority: normal
status: new
---

## Email Content

Hi, I'm interested in your services...

## Suggested Actions

- [ ] Review and categorize
- [ ] Assign to appropriate agent
- [ ] Create response draft
```

## Workflow

1. Watchers detect new items (Gmail, WhatsApp, etc.)
2. Create action files in `Inbox/`
3. Agents pick up and process
4. Move to `Needs_Action/` or `Done/`
